  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4463990/" class="title-link">制度、技术和观念：影响言论自由的三个要素</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4463990"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/3708983/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3708983-6.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/3708983/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">冷眼旁观</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-11-14"
      class="main-meta">2010-11-14 19:16:09</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4463990_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  讨论言论自由，特别是将言论自由作为一种具体的政策目标，而不是抽象的价值进行讨论，那么不仅需要注意制度，还要关注技术和观念。  这本书的作者基本走文本和规范研究的路子，虽然用了案例，但还是在讨论制度如何来保障言论自由。就制度层面来说，这本书研究的还是很到位的，...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/4463990/#comments">(2回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">4有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
