    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/64295211/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u64295211-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/64295211/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">光锥之外</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar10 main-title-rating" title="很差"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-11-11"
      class="main-meta">2012-11-11 12:06:55</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5650080_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                         原来是在泛读这本书，总认为自己局限于知识面，这本书有理解障碍。模糊记得这本书上提到的案例，昨天想找出来了解学习。带着问题认真阅读之下，我彻底明白了，译者根本就没有明白原作者在说什么，估计也完全不明白自己翻译出来的是什么，能够把母语说得如此不成人形，两...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5650080/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5650080_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5650080_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





